data.description: Well maintained 3 bed/2 bath in Millard! Newer carpet and paint Large living room and formal dining room. Bright and open kitchen with plenty of cabinets for storage and eat in area. All appliances stay! Cozy fireplace in the family room with LL daylight windows. New french doors open to the beautiful deck & fully fenced back yard great for activities. Nice wide driveway with 2 car garage! Disney elementary in the neighborhood
